==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Taj Mahal
<hw>Taj Ma*hal"</hw> <pr>(t⟦aum⟧j m⟦adot⟧*h⟦aum⟧l")</pr>, <pos>prop.
n.</pos> <ety>[Corruption of Per. <ets>Mumt⟦amac⟧z-i-Ma⟦hsdot⟧al</ets>,
lit., the distinguished one of the palace, fr. Ar.]</ety> <def>A marble
mausoleum built at <city>Agra</city>, <country>India</country>, by the
Mogul Emperor <person>Shah Jahan</person>, in memory of his favorite
wife. In beauty of design and rich decorative detail it is one of the
best examples of Saracenic architecture, and specifically of Mogul
architecture.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

